Dose Modifications . 
A computer-based expert system was developed to ensure compliance with scheduled evaluations and dose modifications . 
A computer-generated program calculated the patient's body-surface area and recommended initial doses , dates for future treatments , and dose modifications or delays based on the toxicity observed for each course Toxicity was graded using ECOG guidelines . 
