The analyses presented in this report focus on 534 patients (349 on study 088001 and 185 on study 088006) who received the 10,1 dose ratio of DZR or PLA to doxorubicin and were randomized before January 14 , 1991 . 
For patients in the DZR and PLA groups , the cumulative doxorubicin dose at cardiac event was plotted using Kaplan-Meier curves and the doses were compared using the log-rank and generalized Wilcoxon tests . 
